<paragraph blockId="17.[136,1451,1198,1294]" pageId="17" pageNumber="218">
Widely distributed in the Neotropics, from 
<collectingCountry box="[662,782,1233,1259]" name="Costa Rica" pageId="17" pageNumber="218">Costa Rica</collectingCountry>
to NE 
<collectingCountry box="[856,970,1233,1259]" name="Argentina" pageId="17" pageNumber="218">Argentina</collectingCountry>
, from 
<collectingCountry box="[1039,1128,1233,1259]" name="Panama" pageId="17" pageNumber="218">Panama</collectingCountry>
so far reported from 
<collectingRegion box="[1358,1451,1233,1259]" country="Panama" name="Chiriqui" pageId="17" pageNumber="218">Chiriqui</collectingRegion>
(Reiner-Drehwald 2005).
</paragraph>
